                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18730303-253-offence-1 t18730303-name-185"></join>John Wood</persName> and others with 89<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 3<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 8<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., with a certain direction in writing to deliver such moneys again <hi rend="italic">to</hi> the said John Wood and others, or any trustees of the <persName id="t18730303-name-186" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18730303-name-186" type="gender" value="indeterminate"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18730303-253-offence-1 t18730303-name-186"></join>Perseverance Birmingham Society</persName>, in violation of good faith did convert the same to his own use.</rs>
